# Redirects for SEO - Netlify/Vercel compatible

# Ensure www to non-www redirect
https://www.wordcounterplusapp.com/*  https://wordcounterplusapp.com/:splat  301!

# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS
http://wordcounterplusapp.com/*  https://wordcounterplusapp.com/:splat  301!
http://www.wordcounterplusapp.com/*  https://wordcounterplusapp.com/:splat  301!

# Remove trailing slashes for consistency (except root)
/*/  /:splat  301!

# Fallback for SPA (must be last)
/*  /index.html  200
